Beneficiary Enrollment

Source: vignettes/articles/beneficiary-enrollment.Rmd
beneficiary-enrollment.Rmd
library(provider)

The Medicare Monthly Enrollment dataset provides current monthly information on the number of Medicare beneficiaries with hospital/medical/prescription drug coverage, available for several geographic areas including national, state/territory, and county. The data can be further broken down by health care delivery (e.g. Original Medicare vs. Medicare Advantage) and includes enrollee counts on a rolling 12-month basis, providing information on yearly trends as well.



Examples

The level argument has three options: National, State, and County.

Setting it to National will return yearly and monthly national totals:

beneficiary_enrollment(level = "National") |> head(10)
#> Error in beneficiary_enrollment(level = "National"): could not find function "beneficiary_enrollment"



Setting level to National and the period argument to Year will return yearly national totals only:

beneficiary_enrollment(level = "National", period = "Year") |> head(10)
#> Error in beneficiary_enrollment(level = "National", period = "Year"): could not find function "beneficiary_enrollment"



Setting level to State and period to Year will return yearly totals for each state:

beneficiary_enrollment(level = "State", period = "Year") |> head(10)
#> Error in beneficiary_enrollment(level = "State", period = "Year"): could not find function "beneficiary_enrollment"



beneficiary_enrollment(level = "State", 
                       period = "Month") |> 
  head(10)
#> Error in beneficiary_enrollment(level = "State", period = "Month"): could not find function "beneficiary_enrollment"



state & county

Select a particular state:

beneficiary_enrollment(period = "Year", 
                       level = "State", 
                       state = "GA") |> 
  head(10)
#> Error in beneficiary_enrollment(period = "Year", level = "State", state = "GA"): could not find function "beneficiary_enrollment"



Each county in that state:

beneficiary_enrollment(period = "Year", 
                       level = "County", 
                       state_name = "Georgia")



Or a particular county:

beneficiary_enrollment(period = "Year", 
                       level = "County", 
                       state = "GA", 
                       county = "Lowndes") |> 
  head(10)
#> Error in beneficiary_enrollment(period = "Year", level = "County", state = "GA", : could not find function "beneficiary_enrollment"



Data Dictionary

Variable Description

year
Year
Indicates the calendar year of Medicare enrollment

month
Month
Indicates the month of Medicare enrollment

state
Beneficiary State
Area of beneficiary residence

county
Beneficiary County
County of beneficiary residence

bene_total
Total Beneficiaries
Count of all Medicare beneficiaries

bene_orig
Original Medicare Beneficiaries
Count of all Original Medicare beneficiaries

bene_ma_oth
Medicare Advantage and Other Health Plan Beneficiaries
Count of all Medicare Advantage and Other Health Plan beneficiaries

bene_aged_total
Total Aged Beneficiaries
Count of Medicare aged beneficiaries

bene_aged_esrd
Aged ESRD Beneficiaries
Count of Medicare aged beneficiaries with End Stage Renal Disease

bene_aged_no_esrd
Aged Beneficiaries Without ESRD
Count of Medicare aged beneficiaries without End Stage Renal Disease

bene_dsb_total
Total Disabled Beneficiaries
Count of Medicare disabled beneficiaries

bene_dsb_esrd
Disabled Beneficiaries with ESRD and ESRD Only Beneficiaries
Count of Medicare disabled beneficiaries with End Stage Renal Disease and beneficiaries with End Stage Renal Disease only

bene_no_esrd
Disabled Beneficiaries Without ESRD
Count of Medicare disabled beneficiaries without End Stage Renal Disease

bene_ab_total
Total Medicare Part A and Part B Beneficiaries
Count of Medicare beneficiaries enrolled in Hospital Insurance (or Part A) and Supplementary Medical Insurance (or Part B)

bene_ab_orig
Original Medicare Part A and Part B Beneficiaries
Count of Original Medicare beneficiaries enrolled in Hospital Insurance (or Part A) and Supplementary Medical Insurance (or Part B)

bene_ab_ma_oth
Medicare Advantage and Other Health Plan Part A and Part B Beneficiaries
Count of Medicare Advantage and Other Health Plan beneficiaries enrolled in Hospital Insurance (or Part A) and Supplementary Medical Insurance (or Part B)

bene_rx_total
Total Medicare Part D beneficiaries
Count of all Medicare Prescription Drug (or Part D) beneficiaries

bene_rx_pdp
Total Medicare Prescription Drug Plan beneficiaries
Count of Medicare Prescription Drug (or Part D) beneficiaries enrolled in a Prescription Drug Plan

bene_rx_mapd
Total Medicare Advantage Prescription Drug Plan beneficiaries
Count of Medicare Prescription Drug (or Part D) beneficiaries enrolled in a Medicare Advantage Prescription Drug plan
